These days, many people are thinking that there is no need to go out for a live performance like shows or concerts, because watching it at home on TV or a computer screen is better. While other people believe that going to a real-time live concert is a better choice. In this essay, I will express my opinion, which believes that it is a better choice to go out and watch. Meanwhile talking about both sides.

Firstly, watching live performances at home has a great point is convenience. Especially when people really need to use the restroom or have a snack. Furthermore, it costs less and it is fast. Most live performances will be filled with people, so it will take a long time to complete. However, this will also lead to a less exciting experience. That is because due to technical problems, and the size for a TV or a computer. Even though the convenience is a merit. But the loss is greater than advantages in my opinion.

Watching live performance in real site has the best experience for most people. Because people can socialize with other people that holds the same hobbies and have fun together with thousands of people. People can also receive the information about the concert or shows better because it is all real instead of a screen. Thanks to the government on giving us a lot of foundation to create a better experience to watch and sorted so many high quality actors or singers. These matters above will create a more unforgettable time. Although the disadvatages for croudness and expense, it is a winning choice in my opinion.

In conclusion, it is a better choice to go out and see the performance in real time and it will be a well move for your future when you talk about the performance and it is not just a TV screen. 